WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:02.790 --> 00:00:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:05.090 --> 00:00:06.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:06.510 --> 00:00:07.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're coming.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:08.380 --> 00:00:09.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaches]</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:10.010 --> 00:00:11.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
It's chaos.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:12.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-The whole Sovereignty.
-[MISMIS] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:15.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The area around the palace</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:15.180 --> 00:00:17.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is packed with
civilians and reporters.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:17.890 --> 00:00:19.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>News outlets are talking about</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:19.390 --> 00:00:21.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how shocking
the Imperial attacks were.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:24.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not true!
It wasn't just the Empire!</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:25.030 --> 00:00:26.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
The Queen was injured.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:28.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Members of the royal family
have gone missing.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:29.150 --> 00:00:31.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is true that the Empire
carried out an attack,</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:32.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but there's more to it.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They left out the masterminds.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:36.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Both Hydra and Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:37.290 --> 00:00:39.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because we're the only
ones who know the truth.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:40.250 --> 00:00:42.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now everything's going
according to their plan.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:42.630 --> 00:00:43.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:45.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should be careful.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:47.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are Hydra soldiers
in the crowd.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:47.630 --> 00:00:50.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we go, I think
they'd spot us instantly.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:50.470 --> 00:00:51.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, we should lay low.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:54.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're such a big group,
they'd notice us regardless.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:00:54.930 --> 00:00:56.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lou's house was destroyed.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:00:56.560 --> 00:00:59.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the city's being surveilled
by Hydra's assassins.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:00:59.850 --> 00:01:01.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you guys think
we should do?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:02.190 --> 00:01:03.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at this headline.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:06.020 --> 00:01:07.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YUMILECIA]
Can you believe this?</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:09.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Queen injured.
Will she be replaced?"</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please tell me
none of this is real.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:11.990 --> 00:01:14.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even the news has been
co-opted by Hydra?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:14.780 --> 00:01:16.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there anywhere
we can hide for now?</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:16.910 --> 00:01:19.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:20.540 --> 00:01:22.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We don't have access
to rations or supplies here.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:23.420 --> 00:01:25.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So we can't stay in the forest.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:25.210 --> 00:01:26.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, honestly,</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:26.340 --> 00:01:28.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're all dead
on our feet at the moment.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:28.590 --> 00:01:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess we don't have a choice.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:30.510 --> 00:01:32.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should shelter in
one of Lou's safe houses.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:01:33.430 --> 00:01:35.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, the safe houses
you prepared</b></Default>

c0000042
00:01:35.140 --> 00:01:37.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in case
the Imperial Army attacked?</b></Default>

c0000043
00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:40.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I dunno. Are you sure
they'd take Imperial soldiers?</b></Default>

c0000044
00:01:40.890 --> 00:01:42.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[CYSTEA]
Consider this part of the deal.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:01:43.230 --> 00:01:45.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just bring Lady Sisbell back.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:01:45.400 --> 00:01:47.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And trust me,
if you break your promise.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:01:47.980 --> 00:01:49.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're entitled
to take my life.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:01:50.190 --> 00:01:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you think
we haven't left yet?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:54.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're here to bring
Lady Sisbell back alive.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:01:55.070 --> 00:01:56.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You had better.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:57.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We won't forget.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:01:57.580 --> 00:01:58.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
Let's to the safe house.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:02:00.660 --> 00:02:01.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Follow us this way.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:02:04.670 --> 00:02:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A message for the Acting Queen.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:02:06.540 --> 00:02:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RECLAIM: THE WORLD RISES</b></Default>

c0000056
00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:09.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have extinguished
the fire in the castle.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:11.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're still
searching the grounds,</b></Default>

c0000058
00:02:11.550 --> 00:02:13.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but there's still
no sign of the enemy, yet.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:15.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, good sir.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:18.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Imperial soldiers
could be hiding anywhere.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:02:18.890 --> 00:02:20.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Minister, proceed with care.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:02:21.350 --> 00:02:22.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MINISTER 1]
Yes, of course.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:02:23.690 --> 00:02:25.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps receding]</b></Default>

c0000064
00:02:25.850 --> 00:02:27.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can't find them.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:02:27.230 --> 00:02:29.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's highly unlikely
they've gone anywhere.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:02:30.030 --> 00:02:31.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Several members
of the royal family,</b></Default>

c0000067
00:02:31.820 --> 00:02:33.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>including Lady Elletear,
have gone missing.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:02:34.490 --> 00:02:36.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We believe the Imperial Army
has taken them.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:39.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems the Empire wanted
to leave with haste</b></Default>

c0000070
00:02:39.410 --> 00:02:40.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after getting
what they came for.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:42.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If anything was left behind,</b></Default>

c0000072
00:02:42.500 --> 00:02:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it'd be listening devices
and bombs, not soldiers.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're combing
every corner of the building</b></Default>

c0000074
00:02:47.630 --> 00:02:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to find and remove them.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:02:49.090 --> 00:02:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:02:50.420 --> 00:02:51.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My Lady Alice,</b></Default>

c0000077
00:02:51.710 --> 00:02:53.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you did
everything you could, ma'am.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:55.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Try not to beat yourself up.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:02:57.140 --> 00:02:59.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry.
I regret not.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:03:00.390 --> 00:03:01.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do what must be done.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:03:01.850 --> 00:03:03.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First, I'll secure the palace.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:03:03.770 --> 00:03:06.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then address the people
and quell their anxieties.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:08.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plot out our countermeasures.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:09.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But above all...</b></Default>

c0000085
00:03:09.650 --> 00:03:10.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Devise and execute a plan</b></Default>

c0000086
00:03:11.020 --> 00:03:13.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to rescue Lady Sisbell
from the Hydras.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:03:13.900 --> 00:03:15.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
What a terrible mess we're in.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:03:15.990 --> 00:03:18.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's even worse
than 30 years ago.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:03:18.160 --> 00:03:19.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:20.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Masked Lord.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:03:20.870 --> 00:03:21.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You look disheveled.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:03:22.700 --> 00:03:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I've been quite busy.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:03:24.910 --> 00:03:27.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was having a bit of a tango
with a young lady.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:29.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's a Saint Disciple.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:03:29.750 --> 00:03:31.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now then...
I have urgent matters</b></Default>

c0000096
00:03:31.710 --> 00:03:33.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to report to the acting Queen.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:03:33.710 --> 00:03:36.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Tower of Moon is
free of Imperial scum.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:39.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although we still need to see
if they left any gifts.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:03:39.930 --> 00:03:41.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good, glad you're all right.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:03:41.760 --> 00:03:42.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"All right?"</b></Default>

c0000101
00:03:43.020 --> 00:03:45.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid you
misunderstand me, your grace.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:03:46.100 --> 00:03:47.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Royal Palace</b></Default>

c0000103
00:03:47.310 --> 00:03:49.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has been trampled
by the Empire,</b></Default>

c0000104
00:03:49.230 --> 00:03:51.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>beautiful gardens
reduced to ash.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:03:51.770 --> 00:03:54.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The blood of our comrades
soaks the earth,</b></Default>

c0000106
00:03:54.190 --> 00:03:56.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and many members
of the royal family are gone.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:03:56.900 --> 00:03:58.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That includes Growley.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:03:59.820 --> 00:04:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The people are filled
with anxiety and rage.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:04:02.740 --> 00:04:05.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How does any of this
seem "all right" to you?</b></Default>

c0000110
00:04:06.290 --> 00:04:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Zoa's have been
consistent in their word.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:04:09.170 --> 00:04:11.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Advised the Queen
to attack the Empire first.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:04:12.090 --> 00:04:13.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she continued to refuse.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:04:14.090 --> 00:04:16.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now you see
where that's gotten us.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:04:16.550 --> 00:04:17.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The people have spoken,</b></Default>

c0000115
00:04:18.090 --> 00:04:20.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and they pine for a new Queen.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:04:21.090 --> 00:04:22.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that can wait.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:04:22.260 --> 00:04:23.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The House of Zoa
must prioritize</b></Default>

c0000118
00:04:24.060 --> 00:04:25.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>searching for our family head.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:04:26.180 --> 00:04:27.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's still
the question of intent.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:04:28.020 --> 00:04:29.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh.
Which means?</b></Default>

c0000121
00:04:29.390 --> 00:04:30.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[TALISMAN] Hello.
-[ALICE] Hm.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:32.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm late. Forgive me.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:04:32.980 --> 00:04:34.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Stay calm.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:04:34.610 --> 00:04:36.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dear, I heard what happened.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:04:36.940 --> 00:04:39.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I simply can't imagine
what you're going through.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:04:39.570 --> 00:04:41.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The thought of Lady Elletear
and Lady Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000127
00:04:41.870 --> 00:04:43.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>going missing
just breaks my heart.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:04:43.870 --> 00:04:45.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're my dear friends,
as you know.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:04:46.250 --> 00:04:48.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall pray
for their safe return.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:50.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well,</b></Default>

c0000131
00:04:50.250 --> 00:04:51.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't thank you enough.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:04:52.380 --> 00:04:53.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, yes.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:04:53.750 --> 00:04:54.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Speaking of safe,</b></Default>

c0000134
00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:56.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're glad you're doing well,
My Lord.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:04:57.380 --> 00:04:59.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the rumors are
to be believed,</b></Default>

c0000136
00:04:59.420 --> 00:05:02.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the House of Hydra avoided
conflict with the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there any truth
to this hearsay?</b></Default>

c0000138
00:05:05.260 --> 00:05:07.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes!
It seems the Empire</b></Default>

c0000139
00:05:07.100 --> 00:05:09.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>focused their forces
here at the Royal Palace.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:05:09.690 --> 00:05:10.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's as though
the Hydras weren't</b></Default>

c0000141
00:05:11.060 --> 00:05:12.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even on the Imperial radar.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:05:14.900 --> 00:05:15.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:05:15.980 --> 00:05:17.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, thank goodness
for small mercies.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:20.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Might I ask you a question
while you're here?</b></Default>

c0000145
00:05:20.990 --> 00:05:22.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wouldn't happen to know</b></Default>

c0000146
00:05:22.110 --> 00:05:23.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the whereabouts
of our family head,</b></Default>

c0000147
00:05:23.660 --> 00:05:24.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Growley, would you?</b></Default>

c0000148
00:05:25.080 --> 00:05:26.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heavens no.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:05:26.990 --> 00:05:28.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, the House of Hydra
will assist</b></Default>

c0000150
00:05:28.790 --> 00:05:30.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by sending a search party, too.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:05:30.540 --> 00:05:31.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why, how generous.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:33.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will leave you to it, madam.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:05:34.630 --> 00:05:35.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lo, with the fall of the Queen,</b></Default>

c0000155
00:05:37.710 --> 00:05:40.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this nation will be
understandably shaken.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:42.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though these are trying times,</b></Default>

c0000157
00:05:42.130 --> 00:05:44.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we shall overcome
these adversities together.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:05:44.760 --> 00:05:46.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, thanks.
How thoughtful.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:05:47.260 --> 00:05:48.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Talisman laughs]</b></Default>

c0000160
00:05:50.930 --> 00:05:51.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MINISTER 2]
Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000161
00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:55.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the Queen.
She's awakened.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:05:55.810 --> 00:05:56.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How is she?</b></Default>

c0000163
00:05:57.480 --> 00:05:59.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MINISTER 2] The surgery
on her arm was a success.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:05:59.900 --> 00:06:01.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The anesthetic hasn't worn off,</b></Default>

c0000165
00:06:01.700 --> 00:06:03.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she should be
able to talk well enough.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:05.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm on my way.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:06:06.070 --> 00:06:07.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Go take care of her.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:06:07.990 --> 00:06:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall enact the plans
that we discussed.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:06:11.710 --> 00:06:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
I'm a disappointment.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:06:13.540 --> 00:06:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have I become so blind</b></Default>

c0000171
00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:16.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I didn't see
how weak I've become?</b></Default>

c0000172
00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:19.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am unfit to be our Queen.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:20.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000174
00:06:21.260 --> 00:06:23.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was here but couldn't
protect the palace.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:06:23.550 --> 00:06:25.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As for Elletear and Sisbell,</b></Default>

c0000176
00:06:25.470 --> 00:06:28.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I allowed them to fall
into the hands of the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:06:28.930 --> 00:06:29.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:31.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have some important news.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:06:32.390 --> 00:06:34.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm prepared for any bad news
you could give me.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:35.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And...</b></Default>

c0000181
00:06:35.650 --> 00:06:36.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And for what it's worth,</b></Default>

c0000182
00:06:37.060 --> 00:06:39.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm ready for my daughter to
scold me for all my failures.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:06:40.440 --> 00:06:41.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then listen to me.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:06:42.530 --> 00:06:44.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to get Sisbell back.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:45.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not from the Empire,</b></Default>

c0000186
00:06:45.950 --> 00:06:46.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but from Hydra.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:48.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
What did you say?</b></Default>

c0000188
00:06:49.370 --> 00:06:51.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Hydras were
behind the Empire's attack.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:06:51.700 --> 00:06:52.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was them.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:55.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hydra loyalists disguised
as Imperial soldiers</b></Default>

c0000191
00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>attacked our vacation home.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:06:57.670 --> 00:06:59.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire didn't take Sisbell,</b></Default>

c0000193
00:06:59.670 --> 00:07:00.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:07:01.260 --> 00:07:02.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How can I know this to be true?</b></Default>

c0000195
00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:05.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I swear by my right
to the Queen's succession.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:07:06.760 --> 00:07:08.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They will stop at nothing.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:09.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well,</b></Default>

c0000198
00:07:09.180 --> 00:07:11.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after the Queen's Hall
exploded,</b></Default>

c0000199
00:07:11.310 --> 00:07:13.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had my suspicions
Hydra may have been involved.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:07:14.140 --> 00:07:16.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I wanted
to use Sisbell's power</b></Default>

c0000201
00:07:16.230 --> 00:07:18.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to reveal the true mastermind
behind the attack, but...</b></Default>

c0000202
00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never thought they would
invite the Empire here.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:07:22.900 --> 00:07:24.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's more.
The Lou vacation home.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:07:25.240 --> 00:07:26.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vicchyssoise destroyed it, too.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:07:27.450 --> 00:07:28.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
The people staying there?</b></Default>

c0000206
00:07:28.870 --> 00:07:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're safe.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:07:29.950 --> 00:07:31.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They escaped just in time.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:33.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's great news.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:07:33.790 --> 00:07:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Truth be told,</b></Default>

c0000210
00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if Talisman was
behind these heinous attacks,</b></Default>

c0000211
00:07:37.790 --> 00:07:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we have no proof.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:07:39.080 --> 00:07:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talisman didn't act alone.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:07:41.170 --> 00:07:42.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He didn't bring
the Imperial Army</b></Default>

c0000214
00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:43.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into our home.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:07:44.510 --> 00:07:45.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:07:46.010 --> 00:07:47.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000217
00:07:47.180 --> 00:07:48.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go on.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:07:48.300 --> 00:07:49.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell can testify.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:07:50.100 --> 00:07:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-That's why they kidnapped her,
the Hydras. -[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000220
00:07:55.980 --> 00:07:57.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something was off with her.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:07:57.640 --> 00:07:59.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have sensed it
for a while, now.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:08:00.020 --> 00:08:01.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must have
suspected her too, right?</b></Default>

c0000223
00:08:03.110 --> 00:08:04.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In hindsight,
the signs were there.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:08:05.650 --> 00:08:08.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as Sisbell is safe,
and this is true.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:08:08.950 --> 00:08:11.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can use her astral art
of illumination</b></Default>

c0000226
00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to shed light on Hydra's
treasonous conspiracy.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:08:14.620 --> 00:08:16.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Right.
Rin is already on the move.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:08:17.290 --> 00:08:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as
we find the location,</b></Default>

c0000229
00:08:19.250 --> 00:08:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can bring
Sisbell back unharmed.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:08:21.960 --> 00:08:23.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know the Hydras.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:08:23.460 --> 00:08:25.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you had to make
an educated guess,</b></Default>

c0000232
00:08:25.710 --> 00:08:27.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where do you think
they would hide her?</b></Default>

c0000233
00:08:29.090 --> 00:08:30.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
What's going on?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:08:30.470 --> 00:08:33.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are the Hydras keeping me
locked up as their prisoner?</b></Default>

c0000235
00:08:33.850 --> 00:08:34.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I know!</b></Default>

c0000236
00:08:35.220 --> 00:08:36.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I reenact how I got here,</b></Default>

c0000237
00:08:37.180 --> 00:08:38.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>maybe I can find some clues.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:08:38.980 --> 00:08:39.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Worth a shot!</b></Default>

c0000239
00:08:41.400 --> 00:08:42.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000240
00:08:44.190 --> 00:08:45.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000241
00:08:45.570 --> 00:08:48.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enough with the theatrics!
Show yourself!</b></Default>

c0000242
00:08:48.950 --> 00:08:50.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
You'll pay for this, Hydra.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:08:50.820 --> 00:08:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will make sure
we get Lady Sisbell back.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:08:54.330 --> 00:08:56.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is where they took refuge?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:08:57.700 --> 00:08:58.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door sliding open]</b></Default>

c0000246
00:08:59.540 --> 00:09:01.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's me.
Are you all right?</b></Default>

c0000247
00:09:02.130 --> 00:09:04.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Rin, hey!
-Rin, you're here!</b></Default>

c0000248
00:09:04.800 --> 00:09:06.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I-I am so sorry,</b></Default>

c0000249
00:09:06.710 --> 00:09:08.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they took away Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:09.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Ashe sniffles]
-It'll be fine.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:09:10.430 --> 00:09:11.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll save her.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:09:11.640 --> 00:09:13.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice and the Queen
are glad you're safe.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:09:14.470 --> 00:09:15.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks, that means a lot.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:09:16.390 --> 00:09:17.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Queen is safe.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's good to hear!</b></Default>

c0000256
00:09:19.730 --> 00:09:21.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now don't worry.
Please.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:09:21.980 --> 00:09:24.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice and the Queen
will bring our Sisbell back.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:09:24.820 --> 00:09:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well,
I think you should know...</b></Default>

c0000259
00:09:26.570 --> 00:09:28.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the soldiers who had
escorted Lady Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000260
00:09:28.740 --> 00:09:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are offering their help.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:32.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-hmm.
We'll accept their aid.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:09:32.530 --> 00:09:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can trust them
more than our own.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:09:34.780 --> 00:09:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Where are they?
-There.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:40.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.
Hey Rin!</b></Default>

c0000265
00:09:40.910 --> 00:09:42.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[RIN] Where's Iska?
-Uh?</b></Default>

c0000266
00:09:42.250 --> 00:09:44.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's in the room
at the very back.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:09:44.420 --> 00:09:46.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, but he might be
busy at the moment.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:09:47.300 --> 00:09:48.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[knocking on door]
-Imperial swordsman.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:50.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Break time's come to an end!</b></Default>

c0000270
00:09:50.630 --> 00:09:52.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's me.
Coming in!</b></Default>

c0000271
00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:53.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Is that Rin?</b></Default>

c0000272
00:09:53.970 --> 00:09:55.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, stay put.
I'll be right there.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:09:56.180 --> 00:09:57.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We don't have time!
I can't.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:09:58.020 --> 00:09:59.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Please.
Just give me a minute.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:09:59.980 --> 00:10:01.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Why the delay?</b></Default>

c0000276
00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:03.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you up to in there,
Soldier Boy?</b></Default>

c0000277
00:10:04.060 --> 00:10:06.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] What?
I'm not up to anything!</b></Default>

c0000278
00:10:06.110 --> 00:10:08.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just a little busy
at the moment.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:09.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Show's over!</b></Default>

c0000280
00:10:09.530 --> 00:10:10.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[door slides open]
-I'm coming in!</b></Default>

c0000281
00:10:11.240 --> 00:10:12.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:10:14.780 --> 00:10:16.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jeez, Rin.
I was in the shower.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:10:20.540 --> 00:10:23.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imperial swordsman!</b></Default>

c0000284
00:10:23.750 --> 00:10:24.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You fool!</b></Default>

c0000285
00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:26.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could you let this happen?</b></Default>

c0000286
00:10:26.750 --> 00:10:28.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, I did everything I could!
Let's talk about this!</b></Default>

c0000287
00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:31.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Now I've seen you naked!</b></Default>

c0000288
00:10:32.130 --> 00:10:34.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Flaunting your naked body
like this!</b></Default>

c0000289
00:10:34.550 --> 00:10:36.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Walking around like a pervert!</b></Default>

c0000290
00:10:37.100 --> 00:10:38.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, watch it!</b></Default>

c0000291
00:10:38.220 --> 00:10:40.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Hard not to watch
when you're on full display!</b></Default>

c0000292
00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:42.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm trying to
put some clothes on, here!</b></Default>

c0000293
00:10:43.390 --> 00:10:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. You know I'm only
a 17-year-old girl, right?</b></Default>

c0000294
00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:47.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just a child.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:10:48.070 --> 00:10:49.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You gonna take
responsibility, or what?</b></Default>

c0000296
00:10:50.030 --> 00:10:52.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the one who barged in
without permission!</b></Default>

c0000297
00:10:53.240 --> 00:10:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh!</b></Default>

c0000298
00:10:54.490 --> 00:10:55.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
It's whatever.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:10:55.740 --> 00:10:56.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get dressed.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:10:56.820 --> 00:10:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen, while you do.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:10:59.740 --> 00:11:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Last night, the Imperial Army</b></Default>

c0000302
00:11:01.580 --> 00:11:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>orchestrated an attack
on the Queen's palace.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:05.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. I know.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:11:05.620 --> 00:11:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not just that.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:11:06.790 --> 00:11:07.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice is aware</b></Default>

c0000306
00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:10.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hydra was pulling the strings
behind the scenes.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:11:10.710 --> 00:11:12.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And apparently,
you're the one who told her.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:11:13.380 --> 00:11:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, you're not wrong.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:17.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000310
00:11:22.890 --> 00:11:23.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then...</b></Default>

c0000311
00:11:24.060 --> 00:11:25.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you can probably
guess why I'm here.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:11:26.850 --> 00:11:29.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need your help
rescuing Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:11:29.650 --> 00:11:31.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
You don't have to tell us.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:11:31.900 --> 00:11:34.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll help. That's
the whole reason we're here.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:11:35.860 --> 00:11:37.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello!
You up, Sis?</b></Default>

c0000316
00:11:38.070 --> 00:11:39.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sisbell breathes sharply]</b></Default>

c0000317
00:11:39.370 --> 00:11:40.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[choking]</b></Default>

c0000318
00:11:40.660 --> 00:11:41.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise!</b></Default>

c0000319
00:11:41.990 --> 00:11:44.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you do know
what's going on, right?</b></Default>

c0000320
00:11:44.750 --> 00:11:46.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a shame
you're here all alone.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:11:47.210 --> 00:11:48.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sisbell chuckles softly]</b></Default>

c0000322
00:11:48.670 --> 00:11:50.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you know
they'll come for me, right?</b></Default>

c0000323
00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:52.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Vichyssoise laughs]</b></Default>

c0000324
00:11:52.130 --> 00:11:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE] Who?
Your big sisters?</b></Default>

c0000325
00:11:54.340 --> 00:11:56.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or those greasy lug-heads
from the Empire?</b></Default>

c0000326
00:11:56.630 --> 00:11:57.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[moaning]</b></Default>

c0000327
00:11:58.010 --> 00:11:59.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]
You're a lot tougher</b></Default>

c0000328
00:11:59.720 --> 00:12:01.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than I thought.
Figured you'd be</b></Default>

c0000329
00:12:01.100 --> 00:12:02.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>too scared to function.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you're still just
a big sweetie, aren't ya?</b></Default>

c0000331
00:12:04.930 --> 00:12:07.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>especially compared
to that sister of yours.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:12:07.390 --> 00:12:08.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Vichyssoise gasps]</b></Default>

c0000333
00:12:08.520 --> 00:12:11.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR] Congratulations on
your escape, Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:12:11.440 --> 00:12:12.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You broke out of prison</b></Default>

c0000335
00:12:12.520 --> 00:12:14.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the middle
of all that commotion.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:12:14.440 --> 00:12:15.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Smart move.
-[keys clatter]</b></Default>

c0000337
00:12:15.690 --> 00:12:17.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose you had
nothing to worry about, then.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:12:18.280 --> 00:12:20.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am immensely
jealous of your power.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:23.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With that talent,
it's no wonder you're fearless.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:12:24.290 --> 00:12:25.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, please.
Me?</b></Default>

c0000341
00:12:26.160 --> 00:12:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If one of us
is a fearless monster</b></Default>

c0000342
00:12:27.920 --> 00:12:29.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>worth admiring, it's you.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:12:31.420 --> 00:12:33.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you're not gonna deny
that you're a monster?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:37.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'd better be on my way
to kidnap Sisbell, then.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:12:38.300 --> 00:12:40.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do your job,
but don't hurt her.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:12:40.510 --> 00:12:41.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000347
00:12:41.430 --> 00:12:43.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the point
of this whole operation, then?</b></Default>

c0000348
00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:44.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You betrayed the Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000349
00:12:44.970 --> 00:12:47.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but now you wanna
show mercy to your family?</b></Default>

c0000350
00:12:48.390 --> 00:12:49.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Don't lecture me.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:12:49.940 --> 00:12:52.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the last time
I'll see my family.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:12:52.560 --> 00:12:54.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't a girl
get a little sentimental?</b></Default>

c0000353
00:12:55.030 --> 00:12:56.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000354
00:12:56.240 --> 00:12:57.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, this is just
a love-hate thing.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:12:58.150 --> 00:13:00.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wuv it,
but it makes you weawy mad!</b></Default>

c0000356
00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a freakin' drag, man!</b></Default>

c0000357
00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:03.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you can't
go through with it,</b></Default>

c0000358
00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd be happy to step up and--
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000359
00:13:05.620 --> 00:13:06.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Vichyssoise,</b></Default>

c0000360
00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you lay so much
as a finger on my sister.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:13:10.580 --> 00:13:11.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000362
00:13:12.250 --> 00:13:14.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'll destroy Hydra
right here... -[blood drips]</b></Default>

c0000363
00:13:14.840 --> 00:13:15.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-...right now.
-[blood drips]</b></Default>

c0000364
00:13:16.340 --> 00:13:18.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What, so now you'll betray
my family, too?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:13:19.260 --> 00:13:21.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My cooperation comes
with three conditions.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:23.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as all three are met,</b></Default>

c0000367
00:13:23.930 --> 00:13:26.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can maintain this pleasant
relationship we have, dear.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:13:27.430 --> 00:13:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's better for Lord Talisman.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:13:29.430 --> 00:13:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-And for you.
-[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000370
00:13:31.730 --> 00:13:33.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[laughs]
-Wouldn't that be great?</b></Default>

c0000371
00:13:34.310 --> 00:13:35.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am a monster, after all.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:13:36.980 --> 00:13:38.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just remembered
something gross.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:13:39.030 --> 00:13:40.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sisbell gasps]</b></Default>

c0000374
00:13:40.110 --> 00:13:41.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Sisbell coughs]
-Get up! No time to sit.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shwartz better be all right,
or else...</b></Default>

c0000376
00:13:44.870 --> 00:13:45.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE]
Hm?</b></Default>

c0000377
00:13:46.330 --> 00:13:48.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that old geezer.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's safe,</b></Default>

c0000379
00:13:49.330 --> 00:13:51.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and will stay that way
as long as you do what we say.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:13:52.290 --> 00:13:54.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-And what is that, huh?
-I can't tell you, yet.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:13:54.750 --> 00:13:56.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not until you wake up!</b></Default>

c0000382
00:13:59.970 --> 00:14:01.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MEI]
So much security.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:14:01.930 --> 00:14:03.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did some drunkie
get into a bar-fight?</b></Default>

c0000384
00:14:04.640 --> 00:14:06.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We wanted
to keep the peace, is all.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:14:06.850 --> 00:14:08.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The whole world would
devolve into a panic</b></Default>

c0000386
00:14:08.850 --> 00:14:11.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if the Imperial Army
attacked the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:14.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. But how do the neutral
cities factor into all of this?</b></Default>

c0000388
00:14:15.310 --> 00:14:16.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the Sovereignty is busy,</b></Default>

c0000389
00:14:16.820 --> 00:14:18.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you really think
a detour is necessary</b></Default>

c0000390
00:14:18.780 --> 00:14:19.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to throw them off our tail?</b></Default>

c0000391
00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:22.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But besides that,</b></Default>

c0000392
00:14:22.570 --> 00:14:25.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't the Emperor expecting you
to return immediately?</b></Default>

c0000393
00:14:25.820 --> 00:14:28.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA] Yes, but I'm supposed
to gather intel on my way.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:14:29.240 --> 00:14:31.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>According to the Eight
Great Apostles' vision,</b></Default>

c0000395
00:14:32.540 --> 00:14:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you must wake up soon,
Your Majesty.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:14:34.880 --> 00:14:36.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Things are in motion.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:14:36.630 --> 00:14:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathes shakily]</b></Default>

c0000398
00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:39.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems you were busy.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:14:40.010 --> 00:14:41.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The wheels have been turning</b></Default>

c0000400
00:14:41.380 --> 00:14:44.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while the Eight Great Apostle
Meln was fast asleep.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:14:45.010 --> 00:14:48.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Beware. For the moth that
flies too close to the fire</b></Default>

c0000402
00:14:48.470 --> 00:14:50.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is destined to burn to ashes.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:14:50.640 --> 00:14:54.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That power is far too great
for a human to wield.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[APOSTLE 1]
Will the Sovereignty retaliate?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:14:56.690 --> 00:14:57.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[APOSTLE 2]
Improbable.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:14:57.940 --> 00:15:00.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the Founder's descendants
have any inkling of wit,</b></Default>

c0000407
00:15:01.030 --> 00:15:02.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they will know that
now is not the time</b></Default>

c0000408
00:15:02.740 --> 00:15:03.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to bare their fangs.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:15:04.200 --> 00:15:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[APOSTLE 1]
Between the injured Queen,</b></Default>

c0000410
00:15:05.990 --> 00:15:07.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the captured purebreds,</b></Default>

c0000411
00:15:07.410 --> 00:15:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and a kingdom
of panicked citizens?</b></Default>

c0000412
00:15:09.740 --> 00:15:11.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Their retaliation
will come later.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:15:12.040 --> 00:15:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get a move
on your research, Kelvina.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KELVINA]
With what?</b></Default>

c0000415
00:15:16.210 --> 00:15:19.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A shriveled old tree
has no value as a sample.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:15:19.750 --> 00:15:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Might I ask,</b></Default>

c0000417
00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:22.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has she awakened, yet?</b></Default>

c0000418
00:15:22.670 --> 00:15:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[APOSTLE 2]
Need I remind you,</b></Default>

c0000419
00:15:24.010 --> 00:15:26.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Subject E was
your biggest failure.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:15:26.340 --> 00:15:27.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[APOSTLE 1]
Spare us your questions</b></Default>

c0000421
00:15:27.800 --> 00:15:29.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and make haste
with your research.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:15:29.600 --> 00:15:32.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before your subject
evolves into another monster.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:15:32.430 --> 00:15:35.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KELVINA] Oh?
Then give me a better sample.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:15:35.310 --> 00:15:36.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[APOSTLE 2]
We will give you what you need.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:15:37.230 --> 00:15:40.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your mission is to create
a true witch and nothing more.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:15:40.980 --> 00:15:41.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:15:43.070 --> 00:15:46.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[wind gusting]
-[vehicles revving]</b></Default>

c0000428
00:15:47.070 --> 00:15:48.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JOHAIM]
You must stay here.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:15:48.450 --> 00:15:50.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're heading
to Empire territory.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:15:50.830 --> 00:15:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:15:51.910 --> 00:15:54.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know my place as a prisoner,
you don't have to tell me.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:15:55.750 --> 00:15:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How beautiful.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:15:57.250 --> 00:16:00.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Today, the Sovereignty
is finally overthrown.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:16:00.920 --> 00:16:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is day one.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:16:02.750 --> 00:16:05.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was painful.
So very painful.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:16:06.880 --> 00:16:08.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And yet, I simply couldn't die.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:16:09.470 --> 00:16:10.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You, over there.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:16:10.800 --> 00:16:12.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?
Me? Yes, miss?</b></Default>

c0000439
00:16:13.020 --> 00:16:14.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've a small request for you.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:16:15.560 --> 00:16:17.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can a girl
get some water, please?</b></Default>

c0000441
00:16:18.060 --> 00:16:20.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As you can see,
my body's on fire.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:16:20.940 --> 00:16:21.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000443
00:16:21.900 --> 00:16:23.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can get you
something from our supply.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:25.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, kind sir.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:16:25.820 --> 00:16:27.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

c0000446
00:16:28.280 --> 00:16:29.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
Hello, Lady Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:16:29.700 --> 00:16:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see your communication device
was not confiscated.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:16:33.240 --> 00:16:35.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, your concern
is much appreciated,</b></Default>

c0000449
00:16:35.540 --> 00:16:36.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lord Talisman.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:16:36.870 --> 00:16:38.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was able
to make it out safely.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:16:39.500 --> 00:16:41.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How is the Sovereignty?</b></Default>

c0000452
00:16:41.540 --> 00:16:43.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN] As planned,
it's in total disarray.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:16:44.130 --> 00:16:46.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Imperial Army's offensive
was so effective,</b></Default>

c0000454
00:16:46.630 --> 00:16:49.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Sovereignty has
suffered significant damages.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:16:49.640 --> 00:16:52.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We are about to see
the rise of a new Queen.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:54.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They will hold
an election quite soon.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:16:54.930 --> 00:16:56.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN] Oh.
What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000458
00:16:56.350 --> 00:16:57.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You sound weak.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:16:57.680 --> 00:16:59.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR] Nothing.
You needn't be concerned.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:17:00.270 --> 00:17:03.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN] Ah, to be torn
between a human and a witch.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:17:03.230 --> 00:17:04.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Such sorrow.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:17:04.730 --> 00:17:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ugh!
-What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000463
00:17:06.360 --> 00:17:08.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Elletear breathes shakily]</b></Default>

c0000464
00:17:08.860 --> 00:17:10.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

c0000465
00:17:14.240 --> 00:17:16.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm starving!
Is it time for my snack yet?</b></Default>

c0000466
00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:17.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pardon me, ma'am?</b></Default>

c0000467
00:17:18.210 --> 00:17:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.
That wasn't...</b></Default>

c0000468
00:17:21.540 --> 00:17:22.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elletear!</b></Default>

c0000469
00:17:23.590 --> 00:17:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

c0000470
00:17:26.050 --> 00:17:27.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

c0000471
00:17:27.210 --> 00:17:29.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MINISTER 3]
That's enough, Lady Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:17:30.130 --> 00:17:32.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're on our way
to an important meeting.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:17:32.390 --> 00:17:35.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000474
00:17:37.560 --> 00:17:39.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000475
00:17:50.950 --> 00:17:52.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MINISTER 3]
Princess Aliceliese's</b></Default>

c0000476
00:17:52.320 --> 00:17:53.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>astral art is extraordinary!</b></Default>

c0000477
00:17:54.200 --> 00:17:55.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is the leading candidate
for Queen.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:17:56.330 --> 00:17:57.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MINISTER 4]
I disagree,</b></Default>

c0000479
00:17:57.450 --> 00:17:58.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Sisbell's "illumination"</b></Default>

c0000480
00:17:58.950 --> 00:18:01.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is more fit for a Queen
of this new age.</b></Default>

c0000481
00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[book clatters]
-[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000482
00:18:03.170 --> 00:18:06.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR] Only those with
an extraordinary astral spirit</b></Default>

c0000483
00:18:06.210 --> 00:18:07.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are worthy of praise.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:18:08.170 --> 00:18:11.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This nation is far from
an astral mage's paradise.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:18:12.130 --> 00:18:14.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>God, I hate the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:18:15.720 --> 00:18:18.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I've ever been to them
is a subpar witch.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:18:19.930 --> 00:18:21.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So now, all I want.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:18:23.190 --> 00:18:24.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is to watch it burn.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:18:26.610 --> 00:18:28.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] This building will
serve as our new base.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:18:28.980 --> 00:18:30.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Is it
because the other safe house</b></Default>

c0000491
00:18:30.490 --> 00:18:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was too far from the palace?</b></Default>

c0000492
00:18:31.860 --> 00:18:32.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That would make it much harder</b></Default>

c0000493
00:18:33.030 --> 00:18:34.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to sneak
into Hydra's facilities.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:18:35.410 --> 00:18:38.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That, and it's easier for
Lady Alice to visit here.</b></Default>

c0000495
00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll arrive soon.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:41.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Coming here?</b></Default>

c0000497
00:18:41.460 --> 00:18:43.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should she be leaving
the castle right now?</b></Default>

c0000498
00:18:43.370 --> 00:18:44.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems unwise.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:18:44.880 --> 00:18:46.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, she shouldn't
leave yet.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:18:47.750 --> 00:18:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With the elected Queen
in recovery,</b></Default>

c0000501
00:18:50.050 --> 00:18:51.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice is
working diligently,</b></Default>

c0000502
00:18:51.800 --> 00:18:53.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>day and night, as acting Queen.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:18:54.470 --> 00:18:56.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, Lady Sisbell's life</b></Default>

c0000504
00:18:56.390 --> 00:18:58.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>depends on the success
of our mission.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:18:58.510 --> 00:18:59.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When we get Sisbell back,</b></Default>

c0000506
00:19:00.520 --> 00:19:02.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll be able
to prove Hydra's conspiracy</b></Default>

c0000507
00:19:02.430 --> 00:19:03.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>using her astral art.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:19:04.190 --> 00:19:05.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, sir, that's right.</b></Default>

c0000509
00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:07.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000510
00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You look so exhausted, Rin.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:19:10.650 --> 00:19:13.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because I haven't slept
for over two days, now.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:19:13.450 --> 00:19:14.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her Majesty has fallen.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:19:15.070 --> 00:19:17.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As it stands, Lady Alice
is the acting Queen.</b></Default>

c0000514
00:19:17.950 --> 00:19:20.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And my job is to assist her
night and day.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:19:20.490 --> 00:19:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand your duties.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:19:22.160 --> 00:19:23.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you need rest, too.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:19:23.620 --> 00:19:24.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000518
00:19:25.120 --> 00:19:27.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sir, Lady Alice is
pushing herself.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:19:27.710 --> 00:19:30.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As her servant, I-I can't...</b></Default>

c0000520
00:19:31.130 --> 00:19:32.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give in to...</b></Default>

c0000521
00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:34.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh!</b></Default>

c0000522
00:19:34.470 --> 00:19:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shleep right meow.</b></Default>

c0000523
00:19:36.640 --> 00:19:38.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] You're not
acting like yourself!</b></Default>

c0000524
00:19:38.850 --> 00:19:40.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey!
Pull it together, Rin!</b></Default>

c0000525
00:19:41.220 --> 00:19:42.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice is on her way here,
right?</b></Default>

c0000526
00:19:44.310 --> 00:19:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Please take care of mother.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:19:46.190 --> 00:19:47.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KISASAGE]
Right.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:19:47.350 --> 00:19:49.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door slides opens]</b></Default>

c0000529
00:19:51.860 --> 00:19:52.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

c0000530
00:19:53.690 --> 00:19:55.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a little nervous
to see Iska.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:19:56.320 --> 00:19:57.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And so soon, too.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:19:59.280 --> 00:20:00.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales deeply]</b></Default>

c0000533
00:20:01.080 --> 00:20:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000534
00:20:02.540 --> 00:20:03.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-[card beeps]</b></Default>

c0000535
00:20:03.910 --> 00:20:05.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, Rin, I'm here!</b></Default>

c0000536
00:20:05.710 --> 00:20:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to make you wait!</b></Default>

c0000537
00:20:07.080 --> 00:20:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to plan
a rescue mission.</b></Default>

c0000538
00:20:09.290 --> 00:20:10.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello?</b></Default>

c0000539
00:20:10.710 --> 00:20:13.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was told this was
the strategy meeting room.</b></Default>

c0000540
00:20:13.630 --> 00:20:15.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow.
Iska and Rin, huh?</b></Default>

c0000541
00:20:16.010 --> 00:20:17.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two need to learn
to be more punctual.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:20:18.430 --> 00:20:19.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:20:20.510 --> 00:20:21.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:20:25.100 --> 00:20:26.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000545
00:20:26.600 --> 00:20:27.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, jeez.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:20:28.310 --> 00:20:29.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now that I think about it,</b></Default>

c0000547
00:20:29.900 --> 00:20:32.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't slept at all
in over two...</b></Default>

c0000548
00:20:33.360 --> 00:20:34.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

c0000549
00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:35.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't good.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:20:35.990 --> 00:20:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My lack of sleep is
finally catching up to me.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:20:39.530 --> 00:20:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I can't afford
to doze off right now,</b></Default>

c0000552
00:20:41.950 --> 00:20:44.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but maybe I'll just
lie down for a bit</b></Default>

c0000553
00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until Rin and Iska
show up for the meeting.</b></Default>

c0000554
00:20:46.660 --> 00:20:49.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I'm gonna do is rest
my eyes for a little bit.</b></Default>

c0000555
00:20:49.670 --> 00:20:51.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, and it's only because...</b></Default>

c0000556
00:20:51.630 --> 00:20:53.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the sun's so bright.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:20:57.170 --> 00:20:58.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knocking on door]</b></Default>

c0000558
00:20:58.430 --> 00:20:59.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jhin,
it's time for our meeting.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:21:00.220 --> 00:21:01.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
I'm checking the documents.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:21:01.640 --> 00:21:02.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be right there.</b></Default>

c0000561
00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:06.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Captain Mismis, Nene.
It's meeting time.</b></Default>

c0000562
00:21:06.600 --> 00:21:08.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS] Great,
now I can't find the files!</b></Default>

c0000563
00:21:08.640 --> 00:21:09.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Iska, go on without us.
-Come on,</b></Default>

c0000564
00:21:09.900 --> 00:21:11.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-where the heck did they go?
-We'll be right there.</b></Default>

c0000565
00:21:12.520 --> 00:21:14.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin should go too,
but she's still asleep.</b></Default>

c0000566
00:21:14.570 --> 00:21:15.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[door opens]
-It's fine.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:21:15.730 --> 00:21:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll figure it out soon.</b></Default>

c0000568
00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:20.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000569
00:21:21.950 --> 00:21:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000570
00:21:23.780 --> 00:21:25.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice? Alice, hey!</b></Default>

c0000571
00:21:25.580 --> 00:21:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, are you all right?</b></Default>

c0000572
00:21:27.750 --> 00:21:28.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's out.</b></Default>

c0000573
00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:30.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What fiend did this to her?</b></Default>

c0000574
00:21:30.710 --> 00:21:33.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there a Hydra assassin
in this room somewhere?</b></Default>

c0000575
00:21:34.090 --> 00:21:35.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:21:36.590 --> 00:21:38.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is she just asleep right now?</b></Default>

c0000577
00:21:39.590 --> 00:21:41.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[breathing softly]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000578
00:21:41.930 --> 00:21:43.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Alice, you awake?</b></Default>

c0000579
00:21:44.350 --> 00:21:46.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Rin, come.</b></Default>

c0000580
00:21:46.600 --> 00:21:48.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get in bed with me.</b></Default>

c0000581
00:21:48.100 --> 00:21:49.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh!
-Oh, stop.</b></Default>

c0000582
00:21:50.060 --> 00:21:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Don't fight it, missy!
-[ISKA] Wait a sec!</b></Default>

c0000583
00:21:52.770 --> 00:21:53.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
This is bad.</b></Default>

c0000584
00:21:54.060 --> 00:21:55.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, really, really bad.</b></Default>

c0000585
00:21:58.440 --> 00:21:59.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Alice, we...</b></Default>

c0000586
00:22:00.110 --> 00:22:01.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we shouldn't be
doing this right now!</b></Default>

c0000587
00:22:03.070 --> 00:22:04.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, wow.</b></Default>

c0000588
00:22:05.080 --> 00:22:06.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So warm.</b></Default>

c0000589
00:22:06.330 --> 00:22:07.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're burning up today.</b></Default>

c0000590
00:22:08.290 --> 00:22:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be careful,
I'll burst into flames!</b></Default>

c0000591
00:22:10.330 --> 00:22:12.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice, if you're awake,
can you get off of me?</b></Default>

c0000592
00:22:12.460 --> 00:22:14.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no idea
what you're talking about!</b></Default>

c0000593
00:22:14.420 --> 00:22:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growls]</b></Default>

c0000594
00:22:15.590 --> 00:22:16.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe I fell asleep</b></Default>

c0000595
00:22:16.880 --> 00:22:18.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just as
she's supposed to arrive.</b></Default>

c0000596
00:22:18.670 --> 00:22:19.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, stop.</b></Default>

c0000597
00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:22.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just focus and tidy the room
before Lady Alice gets here.</b></Default>

c0000598
00:22:24.140 --> 00:22:25.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh!</b></Default>

c0000599
00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:28.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000600
00:22:29.680 --> 00:22:31.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imperial soldier.</b></Default>

c0000601
00:22:31.350 --> 00:22:32.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should have known.</b></Default>

c0000602
00:22:32.600 --> 00:22:33.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not that!</b></Default>

c0000603
00:22:33.770 --> 00:22:35.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't said anything yet.</b></Default>

c0000604
00:22:35.730 --> 00:22:37.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I swear,
I didn't do anything to her!</b></Default>

c0000605
00:22:38.030 --> 00:22:40.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was just lying here
on the ground, and I...</b></Default>

c0000606
00:22:40.280 --> 00:22:41.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was just laying like that?</b></Default>

c0000607
00:22:42.110 --> 00:22:43.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah!</b></Default>

c0000608
00:22:43.240 --> 00:22:45.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you just threw yourself
beneath her?</b></Default>

c0000609
00:22:45.320 --> 00:22:47.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A predator, driven by lust.</b></Default>

c0000610
00:22:47.120 --> 00:22:49.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You got handsy with
her irresistibly perfect body,</b></Default>

c0000611
00:22:49.870 --> 00:22:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-didn't you?
-Ah?</b></Default>

c0000612
00:22:51.620 --> 00:22:52.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You got it all wrong, Rin!</b></Default>

c0000613
00:22:52.960 --> 00:22:56.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enough! Get off!
You perv! Let go!</b></Default>

c0000614
00:22:56.130 --> 00:22:57.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Alice is the one hugging me!</b></Default>

c0000615
00:22:58.130 --> 00:22:59.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[RIN] Shut up!
-[ISKA] So, wait.</b></Default>

c0000616
00:23:00.010 --> 00:23:00.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're still having that</b></Default>

c0000617
00:23:00.920 --> 00:23:02.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-strategy meeting, right?
-Not like this, you creep!</b></Default>

c0000618
00:23:07.140 --> 00:23:08.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.
[clears throat]</b></Default>

c0000619
00:23:08.720 --> 00:23:09.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, for now,</b></Default>

c0000620
00:23:10.020 --> 00:23:12.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am officially asking
that you help rescue Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000621
00:23:13.140 --> 00:23:15.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've been saying that
from the start.</b></Default>

c0000622
00:23:15.230 --> 00:23:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been our duty
since her escort began.</b></Default>

c0000623
00:23:18.110 --> 00:23:19.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I also want to make sure</b></Default>

c0000624
00:23:19.320 --> 00:23:20.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know
what our rights are here.</b></Default>

c0000625
00:23:21.320 --> 00:23:23.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] Hydra may have
masterminded this plan,</b></Default>

c0000626
00:23:23.780 --> 00:23:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it was the Imperial Army
who attacked the palace.</b></Default>

c0000627
00:23:26.660 --> 00:23:27.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since that's the case,</b></Default>

c0000628
00:23:28.160 --> 00:23:29.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>anyone you find
with ties to the Empire</b></Default>

c0000629
00:23:30.080 --> 00:23:31.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will be detained.</b></Default>

c0000630
00:23:31.540 --> 00:23:32.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Including us, right?</b></Default>

c0000631
00:23:33.580 --> 00:23:35.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your assessment is correct.</b></Default>

c0000632
00:23:36.380 --> 00:23:38.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>During the battle
at the palace,</b></Default>

c0000633
00:23:38.380 --> 00:23:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>many of our fellow Sovereigns
were injured.</b></Default>

c0000634
00:23:40.840 --> 00:23:42.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or went missing entirely.</b></Default>

c0000635
00:23:43.130 --> 00:23:45.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imperial soldiers deserve
to be executed.</b></Default>

c0000636
00:23:46.090 --> 00:23:48.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter who.
Even Lady Sisbell's escorts.</b></Default>

c0000637
00:23:49.930 --> 00:23:51.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's our public stance.</b></Default>

c0000638
00:23:51.810 --> 00:23:53.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But here's our condition.</b></Default>

c0000639
00:23:54.850 --> 00:23:56.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More a special exception.</b></Default>

c0000640
00:23:56.810 --> 00:23:59.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Normally, we don't show
mercy to Imperial soldiers.</b></Default>

c0000641
00:23:59.900 --> 00:24:01.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we've made
this exception for you.</b></Default>

c0000642
00:24:01.940 --> 00:24:04.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>While you're in the search
party for Lady Sisbell,</b></Default>

c0000643
00:24:04.280 --> 00:24:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll keep you safe.</b></Default>

c0000644
00:24:05.610 --> 00:24:07.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was that to your liking?</b></Default>

c0000645
00:24:07.240 --> 00:24:08.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000646
00:24:08.320 --> 00:24:10.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're able to rescue
Sisbell as we agreed,</b></Default>

c0000647
00:24:11.240 --> 00:24:13.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we will ensure your safety
until you cross the border.</b></Default>

c0000648
00:24:14.580 --> 00:24:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Captain.
You accept?</b></Default>

c0000649
00:24:16.540 --> 00:24:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000650
00:24:17.620 --> 00:24:19.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's always been our plan.</b></Default>

c0000651
00:24:19.590 --> 00:24:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Everybody, you in?
